Function for creating dataset with given random values for specified variables

Source: R/dsR.R
dsR.Rd

Function for creating dataset with given random values for specified variables

Usage

dsR(vr = "ms:3;bi:4;ii:1", nr = 100)

Arguments

vr

Array of variables with types for creating a data frame.

nr

Number of rows for given dataframe!

Value

dataframe

Examples

dsR(vr="ms:3;bi:4;ii:1", nr=100);
